summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the improvement of HARBOR AVENUE SOUTHWEST from approximately 140 feet southerly of vacated Southwest Hanford Street to Southwest Florida Street; and a certain other street, avenue, alley and easements, by constructing sanitary sewers and otherwise improving the same, as authorized by Ordinance No. 100573, creating Local Improvement District No. 6520, increasing the Sewer Fund aid to said Local Improvement District and amending Section 2 of said ordinance.
